{"tid":794834,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"都會駅呎價8954將軍澳新高","createTime":"2018-08-26T14:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T17:13:16.000Z","uid":65789,"like":65,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"40d1e5ac2333856b1e33cd60bfff95f9f2a4fac0","tid":794834,"uid":65789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:13:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20100101/large/B03_03_a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20100101%2Flarge%2FB03_03_a.gif&h=b1fc047f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2010年01月01日<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港樓價長升長有，將軍澳區私人屋苑樓價，更已升至豪宅價水平。座落調景嶺站上蓋的都會駅，一個頂層連平台特色戶，成交呎價高達8954元，成為將軍澳歷來最貴住宅。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n1329呎特色戶　1190萬成交<br />\n<br />\n美聯物業高級區域經理方思賢表示，該創出將軍澳新高呎價單位，為都會駅2座頂層G室，1329方呎，客廳外連266方呎平台，剛以1190萬元售出，呎價8954元，不但較屋苑普通分層戶平均呎價約5100元，高出75.6%，並創出將軍澳新高。而同等樓價，更夠買九龍站漾日居單位。買家為同屋苑業主，購入換樓。<br />\n<br />\n方思賢稱，由於全屋苑只有四個同類特色戶，故買家不惜以高價購入心頭好。原業主去年5月以990萬元購入，持貨年多獲利200萬元，升值20.2%。<br />\n都會駅同類放盤現時只得5座頂層G室，面積相同，業主叫價1300萬元，呎價9782元。另外，都會駅是現時將軍澳第二最貴住宅，平均呎價5100元，只較首都5119元稍低。<br />\n樓市在09年底仍大旺，買家趕過年前入市，將軍澳上月錄得多達320宗成交，與11月高位相若，維景灣畔及新都城最旺，各佔40宗；都會駅則錄得23宗，9座中高層B室，974方呎，剛以498萬元售出，呎價5113元。<br />\n<br />\n方思賢又指，相對市區樓，將軍澳樓價明顯落後，市況又旺，區內有逾一成業主反價，加幅3至5%。都會駅1座中層G室，638方呎，原叫價350萬元，現加價4.3%至365萬元，呎價5721元。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  原來以前d新樓可以4000蚊呎"},{"pid":"d813d3fd24c9b242a57e2ada6def641d4405823b","tid":794834,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:16:17.000Z","msg":"仆街<br />\n當人工X2都應該係8-9000"},{"pid":"da0797e754227673ed1f0ce2ed487fe8d157ddee","tid":794834,"uid":18999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:17:22.000Z","msg":"慢慢變番以前<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7005e120f625bf9083ce0e42b24cf3c0aa224e","tid":794834,"uid":126325,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:19:40.000Z","msg":"以前買樓咁平既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015f23ec11a30fe40b86ab2ea1eaf697060095bc","tid":794834,"uid":65789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:20:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n地鐵站上蓋都係$4500呎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而加升到幾多？"},{"pid":"c169fc14f2528a6780b16c348b654c0ad9e42f01","tid":794834,"uid":65789,"like":42,"dislike":3,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"bd7005e120f625bf9083ce0e42b24cf3c0aa224e","tid":794834,"uid":126325,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:19:40.000Z","msg":"以前買樓咁平既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:21:01.000Z","msg":"當時人工水平 應該同而加無咩大分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baab1cf7a2d2efe8bebef89375b8e02c58eda3b8","tid":794834,"uid":8257,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:22:58.000Z","msg":"而家前面要加多個1字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n8年黎人工都無升咁多"},{"pid":"df154d480edddd29c97fdf5889e015931eb0624f","tid":794834,"uid":65789,"like":31,"dislike":3,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"ba